brandComInfo.introduce:
Nodus Technologies was founded in 2002 in the US and gradually became a leading provider of electronic payment, e-commerce, and retail business process automation software for small and mid-size companies. Nodus(Suzhou) was founded in 2008, and its main business was to provide software product development services and supports to its parent company in the US.

Nodus was acquired by EVO Payments in 2018, and now Nodus(Suzhou) is the research and development center of EVO Payments in China. 

EVO Payments (NASDAQ: EVOP) was founded in 1989, and now is a leading payment softwares and services provider, operating with offices throughout North and South America and Europe. As a fully integrated merchant acquirer and payment processor in over 50 markets and 150 currencies worldwide, EVO provides competitive solutions that promote business growth, increase customer loyalty, and enhance data security in the markets it serves.

We are united by a singular purpose: to exceed the expectations of our customers, partners, and team members by being a good global payments processing company.
